Texts.Eng: Ah, the infamous 'dual keyboard' design. It never really caught on.

Texts.Eng: Computer hasss unnecessary amount of buttonsss. Floran baffled.

Texts.Eng: Observant. The more keyboards a console has, the more... nope. Stumped.

Texts.Eng: This computer has more than one keyboard. Seems excessive if you ask me.

Texts.Eng: Why would one ever need two keyboards?
